</span><span class='line'>## 加強安全性
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>如果到這一步，表示你之前都已經完成了!(當然..)
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>請到 [ssl labs](https://www.ssllabs.com/ssltest/index.html)  測試網站安全性
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>沒看錯得到了分數 B !!
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>![level B](/images/posts/2017052303.jpg)
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>感謝網路大神分享文章 [用 nginx 建置一個 A+ 等級的 https 網頁伺服器](https://www.peterdavehello.org/2015/10/build-an-a-plus-best-practice-https-web-server-via-nginx-chinese-version/) 解決labs 指出需改善的問題
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>__1.This server supports weak Diffie-Hellman (DH) key exchange parameters. Grade capped to B.__
</span><span class='line'>&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;h1&gt;使用 openssl 命令產升 4096-bit “Strong” Diffie Hellman Group&lt;/h1&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;p&gt;$ openssl dhparam -out dhparams.pem 4096&lt;/p&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;h1&gt;產生出來的 dhparams.pem 請把它當作你其他的 private key 一樣好好保管&lt;/h1&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;h1&gt;安全起見請調整檔案的owner, group以及權限&lt;/h1&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;p&gt;$ sudo chown www-data:www-data dhparams.pem
</span><span class='line'>$ sudo chmod 400 dhparams.pem&lt;/p&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;h1&gt;/etc/nginx/sites-enabled/myguide.conf&lt;/h1&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;p&gt;server {
</span><span class='line'> # &hellip;
</span><span class='line'> ssl_certificate      /etc/ssl/domain.crt;
</span><span class='line'> ssl_certificate_key  /etc/ssl/domain.key;
</span><span class='line'>+ ssl_dhparam /etc/ssl/dhparams.pem;
</span><span class='line'> # &hellip;
</span><span class='line'>}&lt;/p&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;h1&gt;reload config&lt;/h1&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;p&gt;$ sudo service nginx reload&lt;/p&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;h1&gt;測試成功！！但還是拿到Rank B&lt;/h1&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;
</span><span class='line'>__2.This server's certificate chain is incomplete__
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>這是因為憑證只有最後簽發的，並未包含中間簽核單位的資訊，導致此問題出現
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>憑證是跟 Comodo 購買的所以網站上可找到中間簽核單位的憑證
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>- Intermediate #3 申請的憑證 www_domain_com.crt
</span><span class='line'>- [Intermediate #2 (SHA-2)] Comodo RSA Domain Validation Secure Server CA (https://goo.gl/pNFYR8)
</span><span class='line'>- [Intermediate #1 (SHA-2)] COMODO RSA Certification Authority (https://goo.gl/b32Q0T)
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>接著把 #3, #2, #1 照順序組合在一起變成一個檔案
</span><span class='line'>&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;h1&gt;/etc/nginx/sites-enabled/domain.conf&lt;/h1&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;p&gt;server {
</span><span class='line'> # &hellip;
</span><span class='line'> - ssl_certificate      /etc/ssl/domain.crt;
</span><span class='line'> + ssl_certificate      /etc/ssl/domain_bundle.crt;
</span><span class='line'> # &hellip;
</span><span class='line'>}</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>

<p>以上問題都調整完之後，再測試一次，終於會得 A+</p>

